{"article_id":"WD4PrknyAZ3QuTC8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House could vote as early as this week on plan","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to avert shutdown","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and defund Obamacare","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Senate unlikely to go along with any proposal","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that does not fund health care law","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"House Republican leaders are considering a vote this week on a short-term spending bill","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to keep the government running","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and defund Obamacare ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"according to senior House GOP aides ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"a move","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that increases the possibility of a government shutdown .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner and other top House GOP leaders have been struggling to avoid a showdown over the health care law","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"spearheaded by President Barack Obama","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"and funding legislation","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that needs approval before the end of the fiscal year on September 30","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to avoid a shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"But their proposed alternative strategy unraveled last week","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"after a sizable chunk of their members threatened to defeat the stop-gap measure","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"because it did not directly link continued government funding with a ban on money for the new health care law .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The reversal demonstrates the continued inability of Boehner","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to round up hard line conservatives","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who insist","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"the spending bill prohibit all Obamacare funding .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Can a government shutdown be averted ?","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Can a government shutdown be averted ?","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"01:43","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"`` No decisions have been made ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"or will be made ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"until House Republican members meet","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and talk tomorrow , ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Boehner 's spokesman Michael Steel told CNN .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"House Republicans are scheduled to discuss the next steps on a vote on the `` continuing resolution '' Wednesday morning ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"but GOP aides are targeting a Friday vote on a measure","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"to fund the government through mid-December .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"The measure is unlikely to go far in the Senate","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"because majority Democrats have made it clear","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"any effort","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"to defund the new health care law","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"is a non-starter .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"A senior House GOP aide expects Senate Democrats to strip the Obamacare defunding language","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and potentially send the spending bill back to the House with other changes .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid invoked Albert Einstein 's definition of insanity","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"when referring to House Republicans on Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"accusing them of doing the same thing over and over","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"-- trying to defund Obamacare --","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and expecting a different result .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` They 're obsessed with a bill","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"that passed four years ago ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"a bill","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that was declared constitutional by the Supreme Court of the United States .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"They ca n't get over that , ''","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Reid said .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Another idea","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"gaining traction ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"which is likely to be brought up","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"as this fight plays out ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"is attaching a one year delay of Obamacare to legislation","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that would raise the nation 's borrowing authority .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"`` I can not remember a time","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"when one faction of one party promises economic chaos","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"if it ca n't get 100 % of what it wants .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"That 's never happened before","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"but that 's what 's happening right now , ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Obama said on Monday .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"`` You have some Republicans in the House of Representatives","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who are promising to shut down the government at the end of the month","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"if they ca n't shut down the Affordable Care Act .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"And","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"if that scheme does n't work ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"some have suggested","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"they wo n't pay the very bills","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"that Congress has run up ,","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"which would cause America to default on its debt for the first time in its history , ''","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Five years later , a distracted president struggles with the economy","depth":4},{"id":79,"text":"Louisiana Republican Rep John Fleming said","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"he 's still awaiting to see details on the end game from GOP leaders","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"on how this plays out","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"as they near the deadline for the end of the fiscal year .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` I 'm not going to support something","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that 's going to boomerang on us , ''","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Fleming said .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"But he added","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that he has a longer term goal .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"the play is on the debt ceiling .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"That 's where I want to attach the full delay of Obamacare for a year to the debt ceiling increase","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"because there 's no shutdown with the debt ceiling , ''","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"he said of a second fiscal issue","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"facing Congress","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"-- raising the nation 's borrowing authority .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Another Louisiana Republican , Rep Steve Scalise , said","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"the battle","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"to defund Obamacare","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"should be waged on both the spending bill and the bill","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"extending the debt limit .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"`` We 're looking at both battles ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"using both tools within our legislative toolbox , ''","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":205,"left":0,"right":204,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":125,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":107,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":105,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":1,"right":104,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":112,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":110,"right":111,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":109,"r